  "note": "Li.Fi swapAndStartBridgeTokensViaNEARIntents (LiFiDiamond) \u2014 swapAndStartBridge -> composite_emit Multicall[ amm::Swap per source SwapData[] leg, bridge::send from BridgeData ]. Swap legs = user's real pre-bridge input; bridge leg = bridged asset + destination. [non-EVM dst -> bridge_recipient Raw from facet bytes32]",
